html:
I really don't care anymore.

Most people are worthless shit.

I don't care about their fates

You gonna be dieing on the street no one will help.

They will rather kick you in the face instead

I've met vey few people of good will in my life

I don't care about their salvation<

And there was a war, there is a war, and there will be war in the future

That's all from me.
title: You're worthless
